	(text "Max current calculation\n12 * historic input current = 5 *  output current + c\nc = losses due to heat, can essentialy be ignored\n2025 max constant current = 400mA\n12 * 0.4 = 5 * oc\noc = 1.042A\nThe lowest max rated current is TPS2116DRL @ 2.5A.\nLowest Max rated current = LMC = 2.5A.\nEfuze Max current = EMC.\nMax constent current = MCC = 1.042.\nMCC < EMC <= LMC"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 241.808 65.024 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "e13b5514-8854-4ff9-905d-4151970cdcf7")
	)
